  "purpose": "Canonical shape of the BCP Dev Per-Lot Output. Combines master Flagship Per-Lot Output columns with the richer satellite (PF) Summary-per-lot columns. Every field carries source, grain, confidence, and compute_status metadata so downstream tools can produce ready/missing checklists or deterministic outputs depending on input availability.",

  "primary_key": ["community", "phase", "lot_type"],
